<lb ed="J" n="0549c09"/>　康熙庚申<note n="0549c0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">年【CB】，<g ref="#CB21166"/>【嘉興】</note><app n="0549c0901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">年</lem><rdg wit="【嘉興】"><g ref="#CB21166"/></rdg></app>大夏月吉旦禾郡楞嚴寺般若坊藏板</note></p></cb:div>
